passages.name: NewsletterSuccess
passages.text: Double-click this passage to edit it.

passages.name: currentlyInsured
passages.text:
<Message>
  Har du allerede reiseforsikring en annen annen plass?
</Message>

<Redirect to="[[errorSize]]"
          when="coInsured > 5"
>
</Redirect>

<SelectAction>
  <Option key="prevInsurance"
          value="contents"
  >
    [[Ja, jeg har reiseforsikring->insurerInput]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="prevInsurance"
          value="false"
  >
    [[Nei, jeg har ikke reiseforsikring->email]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: birthDate
passages.text:
<Message>
  Når er du født?
</Message>

<Response>
  {birthDate}
</Response>

<TextAction placeholder="åååå-mm-dd"
            key="birthDate"
            minvalue="1"
            mask="BirthDate"
            next="[[Fortsett->numberCoInsured]]"
            unit="Fødselsdato (åååå-mm-dd)"
>
</TextAction>

passages.name: numberCoInsured
passages.text:
<Message>
  Toppen! Hvor mange flere vil du at forsikringen skal gjelde for?
</Message>

<Response>
  <when expression="coInsured == 1">
    Meg + {coInsured} annen
  </when>
  <when expression="coInsured > 1">
    Meg + {coInsured} andre
  </when>
  <when expression="coInsured == 0">
    Bare meg
  </when>
</Response>

<NumberAction placeholder="2"
              minvalue="0"
              key="coInsured"
              next="[[Fortsett->currentlyInsured]]"
              unit="andre"
>
  <Tooltip>
    <Title>
      Antall medforsikrede
    </Title>
    <Description>
      F.eks partner, barn eller andre du bor med som skal dekkes. Medforsikrede må bo sammen med deg for å bli dekket av forsikringen din
    </Description>
  </Tooltip>
</NumberAction>

passages.name: youthEligibilityCheck
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[Offer]]"
          key="isYouth"
          value="false"
          when="birthDate.Age > 30 || coInsured > 0"
>
</Redirect>

<Redirect to="[[youth]]"
          when="true"
>
</Redirect>

passages.name: errorSize
passages.text:
<Message>
  Dessverre kan vi bare forsikre maks 6 personer
</Message>

<Message>
  Meld deg gjerne på vårt nyhetsbrev, så blir du blant de første som får vite det når vi kan forsikre hjem med flere enn 6 personer!
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option>
    [[Ja, jeg vil gjerne motta nyhetsbrev->NewsletterSuccess]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: email
passages.text:
<Message>
  Ok! Fyll inn din epostadresse nedenfor for å komme til ditt prisforslag
</Message>

<TextAction placeholder="your.email@here.now"
            mask="Email"
            key="email"
            next="[[Fortsett->youthEligibilityCheck]]"
>
</TextAction>

passages.name: youth
passages.text:
<Message>
  Bonusspørsmål! Siden du er under 31 år er du kvalifisert for vår ungdomsforsikring med en fast pris på XXX kr/mnd. Høres det bra ut?
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option key="isYouth"
          value="true"
  >
    [[Ja, jeg vil gjerne ha ungdomsforsikring->Offer]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="isYouth"
          value="false"
  >
    [[Nei, jeg vil ha vanlig forsikring->Offer]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: insurerInput
passages.text:
<Message>
  I hvilket forsikringsselskap har du din reiseforsikring?
</Message>

<PreviousInsuranceProviderAction next="[[Fortsett->email]]"
                                 skip="[[Okay->email]]"
                                 providers="norwegian"
>
  <Tooltip>
    <Title>
      Nåværende forsikring
    </Title>
    <Description>
      Oppgi ditt nåværende forsikringsselskap, så hjelper vi deg å bytte til Hedvig!
    </Description>
  </Tooltip>
</PreviousInsuranceProviderAction>

passages.name: CreateQuoteError
passages.text: Double-click this passage to edit it.

passages.name: Offer
passages.text:
<Message>
  Toppen! Ditt prisforslag er klart!
</Message>

<GraphQLApi next="[[OfferSuccess]]">
  <Mutation>
    mutation CreateQuoteNorwegianTravel(
			$id: ID!
			$firstName: String!
			$lastName: String!
			$currentInsurer: String
			$birthDate: LocalDate!
			$coInsured: Int!
			$isYouth: Boolean!
			$email: String!
		) {
		  createQuote(input: {
		  	id: $id,
			firstName: $firstName,
			lastName: $lastName,
			currentInsurer: $currentInsurer,
			birthDate: $birthDate,
			norwegianTravel: {
			  coInsured: $coInsured
			  isYouth: $isYouth
			}
			email: $email
		  }) {
			... on CompleteQuote {
			  id
			  insuranceCost {
				monthlyGross {
				  amount
				  currency
				}
				monthlyDiscount {
				  amount
				  currency
				}
				monthlyNet {
				  amount
				  currency
				}
			  }
			}
		  }
  	  	}
  </Mutation>
  <GeneratedVariable key="id"
                     type="uuid"
                     storeas="quoteId"
  >
  </GeneratedVariable>
  <Variable key="firstName"
            from="firstName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="lastName"
            from="lastName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="currentInsurer"
            from="currentInsurer"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="coInsured"
            from="coInsured"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="birthDate"
            from="birthDate"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="isYouth"
            from="isYouth"
            as="boolean"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="email"
            from="email"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Error next="[[CreateQuoteError]]">
  </Error>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.amount"
          as="monthlyGross"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.currency"
          as="monthlyGrossCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.amount"
          as="monthlyNet"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.currency"
          as="monthlyNetCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.amount"
          as="monthlyDiscount"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.currency"
          as="monthlyDiscountCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
</GraphQLApi>

passages.name: Start
passages.text:
<Message>
  Hei! Får vi komme med et kjempebra tilbud til deg? Det tar bare ett minutt
</Message>

<Message>
  Først, hva heter du?
</Message>

<TextActionSet next="[[Continue->birthDate]]">
  <TextAction title="Fornavn"
              placeholder="Hedvig"
              large="true"
              key="firstName"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="Etternavn"
              placeholder="Hedvigsen"
              large="true"
              key="lastName"
  >
  </TextAction>
</TextActionSet>
